# RxPulse public doctor portfolio routes
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT add "/doctors /doctors.html 200" or "/doctors/ /doctors.html 200".
# Cloudflare Pages already serves doctors.html at the clean URL /doctors, and it
# automatically 308-redirects /doctors.html -> /doctors. Rewriting the clean /doctors
# URL back to the .html file fights that canonicalization and produces an infinite
# redirect loop ("The page isn't redirecting properly").
#
# Only the deep, file-less paths below need an explicit SPA-style rewrite so the
# doctors.html shell can read the slug from the URL and load the profile.
/doctors/* /doctors.html 200
/u/* /doctors.html 200
